            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "Chitkara International School believes in holistic development of the students. I have seen my ward growing with an improved confidence and better approach towards studies. The faculty here is always ready to help the students in every possible way. It is indeed the best school in Tricity!!",
          "publisher": {
