        },
        {
          "@type": "Review",
          "itemReviewed": {
            "@type": "School",
            "name": "Chitkara International School - Chandigarh"
          },
          "author": {
            "@type": "Person",
            "name": "Ashman"
          },
          "datePublished": "2024-12-26",
          "reviewRating": {
            "@type": "Rating",
            "ratingValue": "5",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "Recently, I visited CIS for the Regional Adolescent Summit 2024. It was a 2 day event, which was about mental well-being and holistic development of children and adolescents. As a visitor, my experience at CIS was incredible! Right as we entered their school we were astonished by their infrastructure. They set up a bunch of beautiful stalls, each with a different life skill activity teaching us the importance of hospitality and personal skills like self-discipline, self-reflection, confidence etc. As we move forward, they had a great arrangement for breakfast. We then went to their auditorium, where the Summit began. We were taught about different kinds of therapies. After a long session of studying about the therapies, we were served lunch which was again brilliant. Later, we were divided into groups for different sessions and after those the day was ended with evening snacks. Day 2 was just as thrilling. From the stalls to the food, to sessions, everything was truly remarkable. In short, we had a lovely time at CIS, their hospitality is truly admirable.",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
        },
